## Important Notes

1. **Dataset Usage**: The Cityscapes dataset has its own license terms. Users must:
   - Register at https://www.cityscapes-dataset.com/
   - Agree to the dataset's terms of use
   - Comply with all restrictions for academic or commercial use

2. **Model Weights**: Pre-trained model weights may have separate licenses. Please check:
   - Mask2Former model weights licensing
   - Any fine-tuned or modified model distributions

3. **Research Papers**: Academic papers included in this repository are for reference purposes only and remain under their respective publishers' copyrights.

4. **Attribution**: When using this software in academic work, please cite:
   - The original Mask2Former paper
   - The Cityscapes dataset paper
   - Any other relevant papers from the research context

